#. type: Plain text
msgid "Today we are asking you to give us a hand to fund our work in 2018."
msgstr ""
"Avui us demanem que ens doneu un cop de mà per finançar la nostra feina el "
"2018."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**Tails protects thousands of people everyday to be safe online and we\n"
"give out Tails for free because we believe that nobody should have to\n"
"pay to be protected from surveillance and censorship.**\n"
msgstr ""
"**Tails protegeix milers de persones cada dia per mantenir-se fora de perill en línia i nosaltres\n"
"regalem Tails de franc perquè creiem que ningú hauria de\n"
"pagar per estar protegit de la vigilància i la censura.**\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"We've all become used to get content and tools on the Internet without "
"paying for them. But you know that this is the result of users having become "
"the new product. While sharing images and messages online, users generate "
"page and advertisement views &mdash; which in turn generate income, reaching "
"up to several billions of dollars for some companies."
msgstr ""
"Tots ens hem acostumat a obtenir contingut i eines a Internet sense pagar-"
"les. Però aquest és el resultat de que els usuaris s'hagin convertit en el "
"nou producte. Mentre comparteixen imatges i missatges en línia, els usuaris "
"generen visualitzacions de pàgines i anuncis &mdash; que al seu torn generen "
"ingressos, arribant fins a diversos milers de milions de dòlars per a "
"algunes empreses."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"At Tails we will never sell your data, nor send you targeted advertising. "
"And we will never sell our project to a company. We have made this clear in "
"our Social Contract. This contract is our public promise to our users as "
"well as to the rest of the world, and with it, we are affirming a commitment "
"to our beliefs."
msgstr ""
"A Tails mai vendrem les vostres dades, ni us enviarem publicitat dirigida. I "
"mai vendrem el nostre projecte a una empresa. Ho hem deixat clar al nostre "
"Contracte Social. Aquest contracte és la nostra promesa pública tant als "
"nostres usuaris com a la resta del món, i amb ell, estem afirmant un "
"compromís amb les nostres creences."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Being free software is a necessary requirement for our tools to be safe and "
"to protect you as intended. If our source code was closed, there would be no "
"way of actually verifying that our software is trustworthy."
msgstr ""
"El fet de ser programari lliure és un requisit necessari perquè les nostres "
"eines siguin segures i us protegeixin com s'ha previst. Si el nostre codi "
"font es tanqués, no hi hauria manera de verificar que el nostre programari "
"sigui fiable."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Last year we've made it clear [[how much of our overall budget came from "
"government grants|news/why_we_need_donations]] and that, in order to remain "
"independent and to use our money in the best interest of our users, we "
"needed to be able to rely on donations. Our first donation campaign was a "
"big success in that regard: your donations covered nearly one third of our "
"budget of 2017."
msgstr ""
"L'any passat vam deixar clar [[quant del nostre pressupost global provenia "
"de subvencions governamentals|news/why_we_need_donations]] i que, per "
"mantenir-nos independents i utilitzar els nostres diners en el millor "
"interès dels nostres usuaris, havíem de poder confiar en les donacions. La "
"nostra primera campanya de donacions va ser un gran èxit en aquest sentit: "
"les vostres donacions van cobrir gairebé un terç del nostre pressupost del "
"2017."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Our yearly expenses equal 230.000 € on average since 2015 - which is a very "
"small budget compared to the multi billionaire companies and agencies "
"running the surveillance business. Many of us still do a lot of work during "
"their free time."
msgstr ""
"Les nostres despeses anuals equivalen a 230.000 € de mitjana des del 2015, "
"que és un pressupost molt petit en comparació amb les empreses i agències "
"multimilionàries que gestionen el negoci de la vigilància. Molts de "
"nosaltres encara treballem molt durant el nostre temps lliure."

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"While last year's fundraising success was amazing, 2018 will arrive fast and "
"our user base is continuously growing. During 2017 we counted 22.061 boots "
"per day on average. ([[How do we know this?|support/faq#boot-statistics]]) "
"**Many hands make Tails: If each of our users gave $15, our budget for the "
"whole year would be raised within one day.** If we could fund Tails entirely "
"through donations by our users, this would make us independent from "
"government grants."
msgstr ""
"Tot i que l'èxit de recaptació de fons de l'any passat va ser increïble, el "
"2018 arribarà ràpidament i la nostra base d'usuaris creix contínuament. "
"Durant el 2017 hem comptabilitzat 22.061 arrencades diaries de mitjana. "
"([[Com ho sabem?|support/faq#boot-statistics]]) **Moltes mans fan Tails: si "
"cadascun dels nostres usuaris donés 15 dòlars, el nostre pressupost per a "
"tot l'any s'assoliria en un sol dia.** Si poguéssim finançar Tails "
"íntegrament a través de donacions dels nostres usuaris, això ens faria "
"independents de les subvencions governamentals."

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"This image shows the evolution of Tails boots per day since 2013:\n"
"[[!img boots_per_day.png link=\"no\" class=\"top-margin center\" alt=\"Tails boots per\n"
"day increasing steadily from 7000 in December 2013 to 22000 in October 2017\"]]\n"
msgstr ""
"Aquesta imatge mostra l'evolució de les arrencades de Tails per dia des del 2013:\n"
"[[!img boots_per_day.png link=\"no\" class=\"top-margin center\" alt=\"Arrencades de Tails per\n"
"dia augmentant constantment de 7000 el desembre de 2013 a 22000 l'octubre de 2017\"]]\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"**But many of our users could actually get in trouble** if they donated to\n"
"an anti-surveillance tool like Tails. So when donating to Tails you are\n"
"also [[giving a hand to these people|news/who_are_you_helping]] by\n"
"keeping Tails alive. Please consider setting up a yearly or monthly\n"
"donation.\n"
msgstr ""
"**Però molts dels nostres usuaris podrien tenir problemes** si fessin una donació\n"
"a una eina anti-vigilància com Tails. Així que quan feu una donació a Tails\n"
"també esteu [[donant un cop de mà a aquestes persones|news/who_are_you_helping]] per\n"
"mantenint Tails viu. Si us plau, considereu la possibilitat de configurar una donació anual o mensual.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Last year, we received 2.043 individual donations. **If you want Tails to\n"
"survive and be largely independent from government grants, please take a\n"
"minute and <a href=\"https://tails.net/donate/?r=giveahand\">give us a hand</a>!**\n"
msgstr ""
"L'any passat vam rebre 2.043 donacions individuals. **Si voleu que Tails\n"
"sobrevisqui i que es converteixi en gran mesura independent de les subvencions del govern, si us plau, prengueu un\n"
"minut i <a href=\"https://tails.net/donate/index.ca.html?r=giveahand\">doneu-nos un cop de mà</a>!**\n"

